  "label": "Nareth Quell",
  "description": "This individual is an undead of gaunt build, with taupe skin drawn tight over prominent cheekbones and a slightly slack jaw that never fully closes. Gray eyes sit glassy and unfocused beneath brown hair worn in a loose, salt-stiff fall. The hands and forearms show thickened, fissured tissue and darkened nailbeds consistent with prolonged exposure to brine and stone. A ropey ridge of scar tissue circles the neck, forming a permanent collar-line above the clavicles.",
